273
00:32:49,750 --> 00:32:52,499
Uang yang banyak, Latika.

274
00:32:52,500 --> 00:32:54,997
Lalu? Apa kita berhenti mengemis?

275
00:32:54,998 --> 00:32:57,413
Ngemis? Bercanda kamu?

276
00:32:57,414 --> 00:32:59,837
Kita akan tinggal di rumah gede
