00:36:48,535 --> 00:36:50,534
Balik ke sana
dan kita semua mati.

308
00:36:50,535 --> 00:36:52,499
Apa kau udah gila?

309
00:36:52,500 --> 00:36:56,289
Dia nyoba ngambil mata kita!

310
00:36:56,290 --> 00:36:58,071
Ama sendok.

311
00:37:06,500 --> 00:37:10,884
Jangan khawatir padanya. Dia akan baik-baik aja.

312
