Sekadar mengingatkanmu, Jamal.

905
01:44:33,500 --> 01:44:36,500
Jika saja jawabanmu salah,

906
01:44:36,535 --> 01:44:39,465
kau akan kehilangan semuanya.

907
01:44:39,500 --> 01:44:43,500
10 juta rupee milikmu, Jamal.

908
01:44:43,535 --> 01:44:47,465
Ini sebuah peruntungan.

909
01:44:47,500 --> 01:44:51,000
Aku ingin melakukan "telepon teman"

910
01:44:51,035 --> 01:44:54,465
Kau akan tersambungkan.

911
01:44:54,500 --> 01:45:01,500
Kesempatan bantuan terakhir. Kita mulai.

912
01:45:05,535 --> 01:45:10,017
Sudah berdering!

913
01:45:10,052 --> 01:45:14,465
Siapakah dia?

914
01:45:14,500 --> 01:45:20,465
Itu nomor kakakku, namun...

915
01:45:20,500 --> 01:45:26,500
Dia kakak yang akan pergi begitu saja dari pertanyaan 20 juta rupee?

916
01:45:26,535 --> 01:45:33,535
Hanya itu nomor yang aku tahu.

917
01:45:56,505 --> 01:45:59,505
Kau sendirian, Jamal.

918
01:46:01,535 --> 01:46:07,465
Halo?

919
01:46:07,500 --> 01:46:10,465
Helo, Jamal?

920
01:46:10,500 --> 01:46:15,500
Aku rasa itu bukanlah kakakmu.

921
01:46:15,535 --> 01:46:17,465
Siapa di sana...

922
01:46:17,500 --> 01:46:18,500
Nama saya Latika.

923
01:46:18,535 --> 01:46:20,465
Baiklah, Latika.

924
01:46:20,500 --> 01:46:25,500
Kau ingin mendengarkan pertanyaannya sekali lagi?
Dan sekali lagi kujelaskan.

925
01:46:25,535 --> 01:46:31,500
20 juta rupee untuk jawabanmu yang benar,
kau punya 30 detik.

926
01:46:31,535 --> 01:46:38,500
Jamal, tolong bacakan pertanyaannya
pada Latika sekarang.

927
01:46:38,535 --> 01:46:41,465
- Apa ini benar kamu?
- Ya.

928
01:46:41,500 --> 01:46:45,465
Pertanyaannya, Jamal.
Pertanyaannya!

929
01:46:45,500 --> 01:46:48,000
Dalam bukunya Alexandre Dumas, "The Three Musketeers",

930
01:46:48,035 --> 01:46:50,500
dua musketeer bernama Athos dan Porthos.

931
01:46:50,535 --> 01:46:52,465
Siapakah nama dari Musketeer ketiga?

932
01:46:52,500 --> 01:46:59,500
Apakah itu [A] Aramis, [B] Cardinal Richelieu,
[C] D'Artagnan atau [D] Planchet?

933
01:46:59,535 --> 01:47:01,517
15 detik!

934
01:47:01,552 --> 01:47:03,526
Dimana kamu?

935
01:47:03,561 --> 01:47:05,530
Aku aman.

936
01:47:05,565 --> 01:47:07,465
10 detik!

937
01:47:07,500 --> 01:47:13,465
Latika, bagaimana menurutmu?

938
01:47:13,500 --> 01:47:19,500
Aku tidak tahu. Aku nggak pernah tahu.

939
01:47:19,535 --> 01:47:26,535
Jamal, tanpa uangpun...

940
01:47:30,500 --> 01:47:35,500
Kau sekarang benar-benar sendirian, Jamal.

941
01:47:35,557 --> 01:47:42,557
Jawaban akhirmu untuk 20 juta rupee.

942
01:47:51,535 --> 01:47:55,465
[A]

943
01:47:55,500 --> 01:47:58,465
[A] karena?

944
01:47:58,500 --> 01:48:01,510
Hanya... Karena...

945
01:48:02,223 --> 01:48:03,566
Hei, Salim!

946
01:48:07,500 --> 01:48:10,465
Jawaban akhirnya?

947
01:48:10,500 --> 01:48:17,500
Ya, jawaban akhir. [A] Aramis.

948
01:48:19,035 --> 01:48:26,035
Komputer, (speaks Hindi) [A].

949
01:48:27,500 --> 01:48:32,500
Jamal Malik, asisten operator telepon dari Mumbay,

950
01:48:32,535 --> 01:48:35,465
pembantu,

951
01:48:35,500 --> 01:48:38,465
untuk memenangkan 20 juta rupee

952
01:48:38,500 --> 01:48:45,500
kau telah ditanyakan mengenai siapakah Musketeer ketiga
dalam novel karangan Alexander Dumas.

953
01:48:45,535 --> 01:48:52,465
Kau menjawab [A] Aramis.

954
01:48:52,500 --> 01:48:55,500
Yang dimana. Aku harus mengatakan padamu.

955
01:48:55,535 --> 01:49:02,535
Itu jawaban yang benar!

956
01:49:22,535 --> 01:49:29,517
Jamal Malik!

957
01:49:29,552 --> 01:49:36,552
Tuhan Maha Besar.

958
01:49:44,561 --> 01:49:51,561
Sungguh malam yang menakjubkan!

959
01:52:12,500 --> 01:52:15,465
Aku tau kau bakalan nonton.

960
01:52:15,500 --> 01:52:22,500
Dulu kupikir kita hanya bisa bersama setelah mati.

961
01:53:03,535 --> 01:53:08,500
Ini adalah takdir kita.

962
01:53:08,535 --> 01:53:15,535
Cium aku.

963
01:53:18,500 --> 01:53:25,500
[D] Hal itu sudah tertuliskan (takdir)

964
01:53:27,535 --> 01:53:29,500
happy ending isn't it?
:)

965
01:53:29,896 --> 01:53:32,739
what a story...

